description:
Earthjustice is the nation’s leading environmental law organization and has been doing the work since 1971. With the power of the law and some of the most dedicated legal minds, they take on one of the most urgent fights of our time: protecting the planet and its people. Their lawyers defend the earth at no cost because justice should never come with a price tag. If you are able, you can donate here: https://bit.ly/AL-Earthjustice

They rule the ice… but even apex predators can struggle to survive. Explore the secret life of polar bears and the challenges threatening their future on our planet.
